	related: {cognitive load} {physical integration}

	categories: <Design Principles> <Errors>

physical integration

	[1115]
	when items that have to be compared are side by side on the
	screen so people can see both things simultaneously and not
	have to remember something from a previous page or have to
	scroll up or down to find the second item.

	related: {best practices} {cognitive load} {gestalt principles} {mental integration}

	categories: <Design Principles> <Layout>

