	an appropriate size for grasping, suggests pulling it. A
	blinking red light and buzzer suggests a problem and demands
	attention. A chair, by its size, its curvature, its balance,
	and its position, suggests sitting on it.

	An affordance is a desirable property of a user interface -
	software which naturally leads people to take the correct
	steps to accomplish their goals.

